Shiny Assistant is a new AI-powered tool that helps you get things done: you can ask it questions about Shiny, or to create a Shiny application from scratch, or ask it to make changes to an existing application. You can think of it as a knowledgeable colleague who is always ready to help out with your Shiny projects, in both R and in Python.
